## Context7 MCP Server
**MANDATORY:** Use Context7 MCP Server for looking up documentation on any task

**Use Context7 for:**
- Looking up library documentation and API references
- Finding code examples and usage patterns
- Getting up-to-date documentation for any library or framework
- Understanding library features and best practices

**When to use Context7:**
- Before implementing features with external libraries
- When you need current documentation (not just training data)
- When searching for specific API methods or patterns
- When you need code examples for library usage

**Prefer Context7 documentation over web searches or training data for library-specific questions.**
